name: 70th Birthday of Axel Cronstedt
obverse: Bust of Axel Cronstedt facing left.
reverse: Inscription in 5 lines surrounded by 7 stars. Below is the cross of the Timmermans Order.

description: Axel Cronstedt was the governor general of the Timmermans Order.
